          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Some will question Baker’s taste. After all, even certain Mopar fans don’t like the fact the modern Charger has four doors instead of two. Most enthusiasts look down on the Cadillac Escalade as being gaudy. While we don’t know what kind of Hummer Baker purchased, if it was an H2 or H3 those are often ridiculed by off-road enthusiasts for a number of reasons.",
